    <h1 id="h1main">
        New PRESTO Devices
    </h1>
    <br>
    <p id="h1line"> You may start seeing some new PRESTO payment devices on transit systems in the 905 and across GO Transit. Many of our devices are now almost 10 years old, so we’re replacing them with upgraded ones to continue to provide reliable service. The devices have a new look, including larger screens, but the new devices are designed to process one card at a time, so make sure you’re tapping only your PRESTO card against the reader (not your entire wallet filled with cards) to pay your fare.</p>
    
  </div>

