    <div class="col-md-4 col-md-4-set">
      <div class="para">
          <h3>Station Devices</h3>
        <p>These new devices will be installed at select GO and York Region Transit stations. Press the “mode” button to the left of the screen, to check the balance on your card. GO customers can also use the “mode” button to override a default trip or reverse a tap. If you tap on a new device, you can still tap off on an old device, or vice versa.
            <br><br>
            These devices also have an “audio mode” for enhanced accessibility. To activate, just plug in your 3.5mm headset jack to the right of the screen and follow the instructions.</p>
